==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ploy
<hw>Ploy</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Prob. abbrev. fr.
<ets>deploy</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>To form a column from a
line of troops on some designated subdivision; -- the opposite of
<xex>deploy</xex>.</def> <rj><au>Wilhelm.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

